Jenkins Shared Libraries are used for code reusability in Pipeline jobs.
Jenkins Shared Libraries is a collection of Groovy scripts shared between different Jenkins jobs.

                Project_Root_Folder
                |
                |
                |------> vars (FOLDER)
                |        |
                |        |--- FILE_NAME.groovy
                |
                |------> src (FOLDER)
                |        |
                |        |--- FILE_NAME.groovy
                |
                |------> resources
                |        |
                |        |--- FILE_NAME.json
